        "parameters": {
          "width": 344,
          "height": 303,
          "content": "## Testing \n\nTesting can be done with CURL or similar.\n\nFor File posting using Form Data\ncurl -X POST -F file=@filepath.xml <WEBHOOK_URL>\n\nThis can also be tested using the Test workflow"
