        "parameters": {
          "color": 4,
          "width": 496,
          "height": 256,
          "content": "## Response\nWhere possible we will be returning a JSON object.\n```\n{\n  \"status\": \"ok\",\n  \"data\": { // JSON DATA }\n}\n```\nIf there is an error\n```\n{\n  \"status\": \"error\",\n  \"data\": \"error message to display\"\n}\n```"
